headline.main: Pence Jokes With 'Enemy of the People' at Gridiron Dinner
headline.print_headline: Pence Jokes With 'Enemy of the People' at Gridiron Dinner

lead_paragraph: Romell Quioto had a goal in his Major League Soccer debut and the Houston Dynamo scored two first-half goals to beat the defending MLS Cup champion Seattle Sounders 2-1 in a league opener Saturday night.
